reviewText: I like the stories which is the reason I bought it.  My issue is the case says it is a two DVD set.  When I opened it, there was only one disc in the case.  The movies missing are ones I already have.
Really not deserving of the 30 for 30 name.
This is a scam.  All I got was a beat up cardboard sleeve, no dvds, no dvd box, nothing else.  DO NOT ORDER.
Waiting for response ....only received a flattened DVD jacket without any actual DVDs anywhere to be found
Great soccer documentaries for any soccer fan. a MUST buy!!!!
